Description: A set of user interface components to create outstanding 'shiny' apps <https://shiny.posit.co/>,  with
    the power of 'React' 'JavaScript' <https://react.dev/>. Seamlessly support dark and light themes, customize CSS with
    'tailwind' <https://tailwindcss.com/>.
